{"tid":1305837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲警方拘7名中國遊客　疑在墨爾本「職業行乞」","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T04:27:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35ee9ca0e4222b8fbed299295801462d07354dfe","tid":1305837,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"澳洲警方拘7名中國遊客　疑在墨爾本「職業行乞」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466921-20190706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466921-20190706.htm&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnYcyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=ebdc173a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466921-20190706.htm&h=211a23de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466921-20190706.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲警方在墨爾本市中心，拘捕7名持旅遊簽證入境的中國遊客，懷疑他們是「職業乞丐」，在當地行乞。警方表示，估計被捕人士已將部分行乞所得的款項兌換成人民幣，他們有地方居住，並非弱勢群體。警方又表示，澳洲民眾雖然慷慨，但不會容忍這些人的行為。<br />\n<br />\n有警員說，這些中國遊客同屬一個犯罪集團，集團成員曾以旅遊簽證的身份到澳洲，並假裝無家可歸，然後將行乞獲得的金錢送到海外。<br />\n<br />\n墨爾本市長對事件感到驚訝，呼籲民眾不要直接施捨行乞者，應幫助他們尋求協助。"},{"pid":"a1f2c0ccce8e799688ee806427219d70e297f833","tid":1305837,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"係鬼國係高尚職業 人工唔高 蝗蟲無乜同情心<br />\n所以鬼國乞衣衝出國際 <br />\n係鬼國 你可以好自豪咁同人講 我係乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係"},{"pid":"e4d36bcbfaf3e176b7d68d0655913763774c0682","tid":1305837,"uid":260312,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"香港特首俾咗500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6bddb6c0f8f2f971c383a3758ad6e34bab3ea7","tid":1305837,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"香港都好多，報警啲差佬仲會屌柒你攪事"},{"pid":"f13a8da690a7475a3c89b25135dd1e6fa800fb1c","tid":1305837,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike"